{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "两位契约者 第22章 2-2 苏醒之龙",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "奈迪犹的异常原来是因为\\n巴哈姆特企图夺取他的肉体。\\n奈迪犹打算使用精灵秘术\\n独自一人征服巴哈姆特。\\n对此芩罗达十分担忧。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "圣树·上层\\n纷乱之枝",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "唔……看来是我释放了太多力量……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "奈迪犹！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "芩……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "到底发生了什么？\\n你的身体怎么了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "是巴哈姆特……\\n巴哈姆特想要夺走我的身体。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "巴哈姆特？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "对巴哈姆特而言，\\n我不过是其复活计划中的一颗棋子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "失去肉体的巴哈姆特\\n为了在这个世界现身\\n而选择了我的肉体……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "原来如此……\\n那会变成现在这样，\\n是因为你与其重新缔结了契约？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "没错。当年巴哈姆特企图与襁褓之中的我\\n缔结契约并夺取我的肉体。\\n但最后契约失败，其计划也因此落空。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "但晓之圣片改写了那次失败的历史，\\n巴哈姆特的计划也因此得以成功。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "所以现在巴哈姆特才会为了\\n夺取我的肉体而在我体内作乱。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "怎么会这样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "无妨……我一开始就清楚\\n重新缔结契约的后果。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "什么！？\\n你早就料到自己可能会因此\\n被巴哈姆特所控制吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "为什么你不早点告诉我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "只要最终我不被巴哈姆特控制就好。\\n而且，就算告诉你，\\n也只会让你担心而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "是吗……\\n这倒是很像你的作风。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "而且我已经想好了对策。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "巴哈姆特的意识没有肉体，\\n所以只能利用我们之间的契约，\\n潜伏在我的体内。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我记得精灵秘术中有一种方法，\\n可以分离肉体与意识，\\n然后潜入他人的意识这种对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "嗯……这种秘术成功的话\\n可以随心所欲地操纵他人的身体……\\n诶！？你不会是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "嗯。我打算对自己使用这个秘术。\\n潜入自己的意识之中，\\n打败企图控制我的巴哈姆特的意识。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "成功的话，我应该就可以\\n彻底掌控巴哈姆特的力量了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "这样啊……怪不得你会对\\n那个秘术如此在意。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "虽说时机上稍微偏离了计划，\\n但这一刻我已经等了很久，\\n巴哈姆特在我的体内现形的这一刻。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "原来是这样……\\n不愧是奈迪犹……\\n不过，还有一个问题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "就是你能否真的战胜巴哈姆特。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "我很了解你的能力。\\n但对方毕竟是创世之龙，\\n我不能随随便便就答应你这么做。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "那还能怎么办……\\n应该没有别的方法了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "没有必要改变方法。\\n不过，能够使用这个秘术的，\\n并不只有你一个人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "我会与你一同进入\\n你的精神世界，\\n助你打败巴哈姆特。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "芩……你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "怎么样？\\n不觉得这是个好主意吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "抱歉……我拒绝。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "奈迪犹！？为什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这是我自己的事。\\n为了完全掌握巴哈姆特的力量，\\n我必须以一己之力征服巴哈姆特。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "奈迪犹，从秘术的性质上来看，\\n无论打败巴哈姆特的是谁，\\n对结果都不会有影响。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "我们不是约好要一起见证新世界吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这是两码事。\\n我必须要靠自己的力量征服巴哈姆特。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "奈迪犹……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "你果然……\\n还是选择了独自战斗啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "芩，其实我有事情需要麻烦你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_001"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "使用秘术期间，我的身体会毫无防备。\\n因此需要有人在此期间阻止他人的干扰。\\n能让我放心的，就只有你了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "干扰……\\n确实，这个问题必须要解决呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "啊！大家快看！\\n那边有人！我好像找到他们了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_22_02_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}